{"tid":2496894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"錦戶亮疑勾義嫂 大野智帶新歡遊京都準備做老襯","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:16:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"39678f421f161bedb6c0b3787bf492d08f5085df","tid":2496894,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0aFN5JZqbVS4QqAjm5cnxiuhLzY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5XQXPXDTKZDFZPSRNE46QDWG6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0aFN5JZqbVS4QqAjm5cnxiuhLzY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5XQXPXDTKZDFZPSRNE46QDWG6U.jpg&h=a1a0a8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本國民組合嵐的40歲隊長大野智，去年被爆與一名單親媽媽A小姐發展地下情長達六年，當時報道指大野智打算跟女友結婚，戀情亦成了嵐解體的導火線，日媒曾公開兩人的親密合照，當外界還以為大野智榮升後父之際。最近有消息指二人已分手收場，30歲的A小姐還搭上大野智前師弟、36歲的關8舊將錦戶亮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PYU-PvhRBWtZSLdISJDOSKKo2K4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JSPURMZ3C5EQVITCGJZTWN3X2U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPYU-PvhRBWtZSLdISJDOSKKo2K4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJSPURMZ3C5EQVITCGJZTWN3X2U.JPG&h=1e7347cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yuEcFQJ1TSH7JyU3Z5VSfFRzPuU=/802x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3B5AA2WH4NERJKJ3VRD4OAPQGI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyuEcFQJ1TSH7JyU3Z5VSfFRzPuU%3D%2F802x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3B5AA2WH4NERJKJ3VRD4OAPQGI.JPG&h=4ec050f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KDMs4X6SBIo5Gph01PXHP2RzXEs=/802x1257/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWJHX2IT4ZFJ5MHDLNSNBBQ744.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKDMs4X6SBIo5Gph01PXHP2RzXEs%3D%2F802x1257%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWJHX2IT4ZFJ5MHDLNSNBBQ744.JPG&h=089a6cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大野智現正處於休業狀態，有報道指他已開個人公司，密謀離巢後另起爐灶，不排除今後以個人姿態獨立發展。今日出版的《女性自身》報道，跟A小姐分手的大野智原來亦有着落，日前發現他與一名圈外新歡同遊京都，大野今次重遊舊地特別帶女友到相熟旅館享受二人世界，大野智被拍得手搭女友腰間，態度親暱。大野智9年前曾在電視節目上談到適婚年齡，正正就是40歲，令人懷疑他跟新任女友隨時拉埋天窗。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，有關A小姐的是非近期亦相繼流出，一名與她相熟的YouTuber日前爆料，公開大野智與A小姐的沒打格甜蜜照片，使她的廬山真面目及身份全面曝光。A小姐本名叫真理惠，年約30歲，比大野智年輕10載，指她早在前年1月已跟大野智分手，但她上月初又在網上開live談起大野智，引起嵐的fans很大迴響，直指有人想借大野智來博上位，更有嵐fans公開疑似是A小姐的殘爆吸煙截圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BOnt2xGtJc_ityG5FG1cjNeWcfk=/802x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QY3KLGSC4JEQPIUVPWGJQQRFGU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBOnt2xGtJc_ityG5FG1cjNeWcfk%3D%2F802x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQY3KLGSC4JEQPIUVPWGJQQRFGU.JPG&h=1526d43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W04_2iD5HbNwAixfx8DLUifiQSA=/802x536/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NZLUGEHENVDBDATUXKH2JSOWSM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW04_2iD5HbNwAixfx8DLUifiQSA%3D%2F802x536%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNZLUGEHENVDBDATUXKH2JSOWSM.JPG&h=83f228a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4569fe404db3d048b1502cdf08f4e17754aeef1","tid":2496894,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":